Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's Gaki is ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rendezvous without using your smartphones: Special with Takanori Nishikawa and Alice Hirose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Downtown started at Alta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna leave me for a younger woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We will show you the unreleased parts that we had no choice but to cut due to the air time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I watch every show they are on, it's like my obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a different background than they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a meeting of nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We are gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were just trash-talking me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:01:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Subbed by RAIDEN1017]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This segment is not finished until everyone has met, each going to the place they imagine from the theme presented.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were joined by guests Takanori Nishikawa and Alice Hirose, making a total of seven people trying to complete the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if they encounter Matsumoto Iyo, who is the Joker, with two or more members, they have to disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the first theme?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They got into a cab and the game started at 12:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The closest one from here is Juntendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A while ago, when I caught a cold, I used to go to Kosei Chuo in Ebisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:02:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a hospital that is accustomed to dealing with celebrities.\NI think they would come to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I think Sanno Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They headed in their car to their destination to meet with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are plenty of people out there who think I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is a game of majority rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to play this with smart people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They are less educated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what all five of you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they were, I went to Amagasaki Technical High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the mechanical department there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The academic deviation for that is about 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Houssei, always prone to disease, talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me again what illness you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Peyronie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A man's penis has three prostates, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,*At an bar, after Hosei told Matsumoto that he was suffering from the disease, Hosei cried and said something unintelligible: 'I have to cut off my penis. But then I can become a psychic medium.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why my corpus cavernosum is hardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a rare disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One in half a million people get this disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your jaw these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It healed right after we finished recording "Don't Laughing."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nothing hurts?\N- Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I hear there is another "Don't Laughing" recording I will be sick again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What was Matsumoto talking about when he was heading to Juntendo University Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The theme is hospital.\NI haven't been to hospitals much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san likes hospitals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he does.\NBut he often misses work even with a slight fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes very good care of himself, but he is physically and mentally weak.\NThat's why he misses work when it's a little hard for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I rarely miss work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked for about 36 years and have hardly missed a day of work.\NI've only missed two or three days of work because I was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed work a few times because I was sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone arrived at their destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They called to confirm their locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For all intents and purposes, you guys should go to Juntendo Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Juntendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at Tokyo University Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys haven't been watching the news lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at Nihon University Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nihon University Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're in a place like that, you might see former coach Uchida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't meet someone on the theme of hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the second theme?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Places where people who moved to Tokyo go for the first time."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On this theme, they talked about their memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Hamada talked about his first time in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Had you been to Tokyo before you came there on business?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I have.\NBut it was in Kitasenju.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitasenju?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A classmate of mine from high school lived there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed at his house in Kita-Senju with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we went to Ginza for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered what he would treat me to.\NHe said, "Let's have pizza."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to my friend, "What's ‘pizza'?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"What the hell is ‘pizza'?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I ate pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka talked about his memories of Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first came to Tokyo, I had a part-time job in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- What kind of part-time job did you have?\N- I was a waiter at a coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There were many young female customers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I had thick arm hair.\NA customer complained to me, and I had to work in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"He is gross."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"That waiter is gross."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Tokyo was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei, who was heading to Alta, talked about his memories of Waratte-Iitmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever appeared on Waratte-Iitomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I never appeared on the show as a regular, but I appeared a few times as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I appeared in the talk show section with Tamori-san, suddenly an audience asked, "Is it true that this show will end soon? "
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- That was during a recording, right?\N- Yes, it was a live broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,An audience said in a loud voice, "Is it true that this show will end soon? "
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The studio was abuzz.\NThen it went to commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had prepared a lot of topics to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But the commercial break came soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamori-san, the host, said to me, "Your aura must have brought in some strange audience."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He was forced by security to leave during the commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a teddy bear in the seat he was sitting in after the commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Tamori-san's ad-lib.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There used to be a live children's show called Romper Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One kid yelled, "Penis! Penis! Poop! Poop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He was gone after the commercial, and there was a teddy bear in his seat.\NThat happened a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Hirose was talking about his hobby, comics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first met Matsumoto-san, I told him about comics and he was disgusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see people with different tastes from mine as perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you think of Matsumoto-san's muscle training?\N- He is a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:09:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He uploads pictures of his muscles on SNS at the end of the year and at the beginning of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he uploads them on Twitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I think he is a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They chose "Place where people who moved to Tokyo go for the first time" with their own memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosei arrived at Studio Alta in Shinjuku a little earlier than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My memory of this place is Waratte-Iitomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I used to meet up with girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you used to pick up girls in the past?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san would wait in the car and I would talk to the girl I was interested in.\N"Hi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you tell her that Matsumoto-san was in the car?\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"There's Downtown."\N"There's Downtown right there."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:10:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He was talking about his memories of picking up girls when he was younger, but one question came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If Alice-chan had come here, would a lot of people have gathered around her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't gather with me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They really don't gather at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think they're being reserved, don't you?\N- Is that so? Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosei was surprised that he was so unpopular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Matsumoto met up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the topic was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, there's no one here.\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nobody's gathered around you.\N- Oh, is that what you meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- No one is making a fuss.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you came, people have been gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was walking towards here, I thought there would never be any celebrities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If there were a celebrities here, there is no way there would be such a vast space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still meet up with a girl here even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to the staff, "They would leave even if they noticed me or not. Don't you think they're terrible?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he said, "This is how Tokyo is."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is how Tokyo is."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,People are gathering here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was over there thinking, "There will never be any celebrities here."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times are you going to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rendezvous without using your smartphones: Special
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Two pairs were formed under the theme of "Place where people who moved to Tokyo go for the first time".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The next theme was university.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada and Hirose talked about Hirose's private life in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you drive a car?\N- No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where I want to go, so I use a cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- But aren't you limited to the places you can go?\N- Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't go out far.\NIt's too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's nice of you to say "it's too much trouble" when you're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go to more places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I started cooking because it's too much trouble to go out to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There is Meiji University right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you suggesting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we're going to Meiji University on this theme?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, this is rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And what were Matsumoto and Hosei talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought about going to university.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why?\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- You had a job lined up when you were in high school, right?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was it a technical high school?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The deviation was 69.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But the teacher said, "I don't know, but I think that's about right."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't know"?\NHe's a messed up teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you nervous because you thought you might be alone with Nishikawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I had a feeling he might be there when the theme was the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking what I would do if I was alone with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want to be alone with Alice-chan, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm quite a bit older than her, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,More than that, I would have a hard time if someone like Shino-san was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shino Ikenami?\N- She's Nakao-san's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know what to do if I were alone with Shino Ikenami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Natsumi-san? (Hamada's wife)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, I have no choice but to change my mind and do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to consider that it will be aired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I only think about how to make it interesting as show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was Nishikawa talking about at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should do this in a foreign country or in a rural area, although those two would definitely not like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two would dislike working with an overnight stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like doing Strange Town with everyone separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to do Strange Town, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let's do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you watch a lot of this show?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I watch most of their shows because you never know what those two will ask me at any given moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- All the stations?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as much as Inomoto does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you consider yourself as their junior?\N- Yes, I feel the same way as Inomoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I talk to them, I don't say, "Oh, really?" I want to say, " Yeah, of course I know that."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be annoyed if they have to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They could meet 6 people on this theme at the Tokyo University except for Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only place to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all that's left is Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the joker, Iyo Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The six of them must split up.\NThey are back to square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you guys first!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an appointment at 3:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make appointment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I told you guys that.\N- What appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rendezvous without using your smartphones: Special
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting from zero.\NThe fourth theme was department stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:17:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it's pretty hard to make a situation where all seven of us are together and only Iyo-chan is in a different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry for being in a hurry, but let's make Endo the joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everything will be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- If that's the case, we're finished with that earlier.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's re-record the opening and make Endo the joker.\NThen it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to the editors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, Hosei, and Tanaka went to Mitsukoshi in Nihonbashi, while Hamada and Hirose went to Isetan in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto was the first to arrive at Mitsukoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who doesn't come here is a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who doesn't come here is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hi!\N- Oh, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good luck!\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing my best, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's the only place!\N- Yes, it's the only place I can think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of department stores, this is the place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Because this is the first department store in Japan.\N- Yes, from a historical point of view, it's also here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a different background from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can imagine, I don't expect everyone to gather here.\NBut we can share with each other the nobility of our fellowship that has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a meeting of nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We are gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were just trash-talking me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of them met up in Nihonbashi, the city for adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto was pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this part will be aired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is being communicated from us to the viewers.\NI still think we are neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't stop praising themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are virtuous as human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if we are educated or rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not what we are about, we have something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nobility.\N- Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I also consider the balance of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a producer, and I think we need the Nihonbashi as one of the spots to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"You want a scene like this, don't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey director, you want this, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Viewers will want to see many different places. It's a kindness from you to the viewers.\N- Yes, it's kindness and grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So our body odor doesn't stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't smell at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Their body odor just smells bad no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How did Alice Hirose, who chose Isetan in Shinjuku at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She got to meet Hamada again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the result on the theme of department stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo did not meet anyone because things did not go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rendezvous without using your smartphones: Special
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The fifth theme was a golf practice range.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada, who loves golf, went to Jingu Gaien with Hirose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't play golf, so I am not familiar with it. Are there any golf ranges other than Jingu and Kasai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There is Himonya in Meguro, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Jingu Gaien is the most famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This theme is an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo knows all the places I just mentioned.\NSo it's up to him to choose where he wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's up to Nishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to meet Endo-san soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThis is weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen him for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been recording alone all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, what were Matsumoto, Hosei, and Tanaka talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice-chan would love to be alone with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That wish will not come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada is always in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a natural order of the world that has existed since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NThere will always be someone who gets in the way of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a love story is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you turn up the air conditioning a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about Hamada made me feel physically hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice-chan is probably disgusted with Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be sitting in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably getting too close to her
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada will be thinking about touching her whenever he gets a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He is called the last sexual harasser in show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it's said that if he dies, sexual harassment will disappear from the show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, at the Jingu Golf Range...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Matsumoto, Yama-chan and Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All seven successfully met up with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Iyo Matsumoto, the joker, headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Iyo-chan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at Himonya Swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She is in Himonya!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All seven of us are at Jingu Golf Range!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Sanma-san by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you met Sanma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- You met him at Himonya?\N- Apparently, Sanma-san also goes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you look so disappointed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.53,0:23:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If all of us had gone to Himonya, it would have been great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Subbed byRAIDEN1017]
